# 📊 Project SmartQueue: Enterprise Support Triage & Insights Platform

A production-grade customer data intelligence engine designed to ingest unstructured communications, enforce strict data schemas, execute deterministic routing arrays, and visualize live corporate metrics.

## 🚀 Core Functionalities
* **Structured Semantic Extraction:** Constrains local open-source LLM token probabilities to enforce strict JSON syntax outputs, converting chaotic customer emails into clean metadata arrays (Sentiment, Category, Urgency, and Summary).
* **Conditional Business Logic Router:** An automated dispatcher that evaluates extracted metadata blocks against corporate priority frameworks, asynchronously routing payloads to distinct departmental JSON vault queues.
* **Executive Metrics Dashboard:** Built on Streamlit and Pandas to aggregate distributed file queues dynamically, displaying live critical alerts, sentiment analytics, and volumetric queue charts.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
* Python (Streamlit, Pandas, Requests, OS, Glob)
* Ollama (`llama3.2:3b`)